-- Turkey's Bank Asya shares fall 2.9 pct after trading resumed
-- By Seda Sezer
-- Wed Sep 24, 2014 07:21AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, Sept 24 (Reuters) - Shares in Turkey's Bank Asya <ASYAB.IS>, an Islamic finance institution, fell 2.9 percent on Wednesday afternoon as trade resumed following a suspension due to volatility in the price.

